Add @coconut milk{400%ml} and @granulated sugar{200%g} to a #saucepan{}.

Bring the mix to a simmer on medium heat while stirring to dissolve the sugar completely.

Once simmering, bring the heat down to medium-low.

After about ~{25%minutes}, the mixture should have reduced by about a third of from the original volume.

Let the mixture cool to room temperature before storing it in the #fridge.
